#ACTION {A (fragrant-smelling bag|green leather bag|crude herbal kit) contains a handful of narrow leaves, a handful of clover and a man-like root} {#SHOWME {$0 ($p_BOLD$p_HERBCOLTravelling$p_NORM)}}
#CLASS {mixedtrav1} {CLOSE}
