#CLASS {mixedleaf1} {CLOSE}
#CLASS {mixedvenom1} {OPEN}
#ACTION {A (fragrant-smelling bag|green leather bag|crude herbal kit) contains a small fluid-sack, a short, moist tail and some short, black fur} {#SHOWME {$0 ($p_BOLD$p_HERBCOLVenom$p_NORM).}}
#CLASS {mixedvenom1} {CLOSE}
